
Usage:

    {{#cyan}}bower{{/cyan}} list
    {{#cyan}}bower{{/cyan}} ls


Options:

    {{#yellow}}--map{{/yellow}}      - Generates a deep dependency JSON source mapping
    {{#yellow}}--paths{{/yellow}}    - Generates a simple JSON source mapping
    {{#yellow}}--sources{{/yellow}}  - Generates list of source files in order of dependency
    {{#yellow}}--offline{{/yellow}}  - Avoid checking for newer versions
    {{#yellow}}--no-color{{/yellow}} - Do not print colors

